Title: Lucky stop
DateModified: '2019-02-05'
DatePublished: '2019-02-05'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/lucky-stop
SetInCountry: Indonesia
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Irene Diaz
AuthorCountry: Spain
Text: "A teenager stop me while was driving my moto, invite me to watch a match together\
  \ and finish going to visit his family and expend couple of days in their house\
  \ like another member of the family, visiting their other family in different towns,\
  \ helping with the children... living like a really local. \nWas amazing have the\
  \ opportunity of live in a real and non touristic family in a random and small town\
  \ from the road."
